- Use Day.js plugins for additional functionality (e.g., timezone support)
- Implement proper locale handling for internationalization
- Utilize Day.js' formatting options for consistent date display
- Avoid mutating dates directly; use Day.js' immutable methods
- Create utility functions for common date operations
- Handle timezone conversions properly
- Use proper date parsing for user inputs
- Implement consistent date formatting across the application 